Functional Requirements
Users can submit network requests through the Service Catalog.
Dynamic fields appear based on request type.
Requests are validated before submission.
Approval workflow is automatically triggered.
Fulfillment tasks are created after approval.
Email notifications are sent during each stage.
Users can track request status.
Reports and dashboards display request analytics.
Non-Functional Requirements
Secure access using role-based permissions.
High availability and scalability.
Fast request processing.
Audit-ready request history.
User-friendly interface.
User Roles
Requester
Approver
Network Team
Administrator
